{"tid":2351493,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"有位法國人喺日本新宿站出面聲援香港","createTime":"2021-01-03T08:59:25.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-03T15:14:43.000Z","uid":42375,"like":118,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"a62655abe51e1e56475168d3db59571bd7efd77e","tid":2351493,"uid":42375,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-03T08:59:25.000Z","msg":"呢位法國手足叫Leo,前兩日佢pm香港建國聯盟，話想做街宣，聯盟代表就幫佢同日本警方交涉，當然警方都好奇怪，點解會幫一個素未謀面嘅人申請街宣。為免有伏，代表只係去幫佢影相同傾偈，並冇其他成員參與。<br />\n<br />\n傾咗一陣，Leo寄語香港人唔好放棄，仲有好多人支持我哋。最後街宣冇俾中國人搗亂，好多日本人都過嚟打氣同捐款。代表就去同佢飲杯咖啡，送咗枝獨立旗俾Leo做紀念品，希望以後為香港，一齊努力。<br />\n<br />\n附上link,可以去多謝Leo手足<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/leotaoki/status/1345639863601623040?s=21\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fleotaoki%2Fstatus%2F1345639863601623040%3Fs%3D21&d=r3XH83vhlb%2FNbb5A40Y%2F0J2AEL7eB1GKmMTTK1c2%2F04%3D&h=6b9180b1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fleotaoki%2Fstatus%2F1345639863601623040%3Fs%3D21&h=0c62759c\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/leotaoki/status/1345639863601623040?s=21</a>"},{"pid":"bdafee1e1bc3782770cfba60954e762c2172e7b2","tid":2351493,"uid":42375,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-03T09:02:37.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"487f6755ef9b98d56c6f0208b438253f19a378d8","tid":2351493,"uid":91397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-03T09:04:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f5d5b8adb50726fc6909ddfeeeb908727fd5e44","tid":2351493,"uid":91397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-03T09:04:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1fa614aa14620adffeec1d1d6da3ddefd53523d1","tid":2351493,"uid":47462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-03T09:04:23.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b04900f54b4ebc0f0d56d9b8c272c175df8c02f2